root: ^(If it was me, I'd easily choose to retire in this farmhouse)
^(This house will definitely play into their love of gardening and they did mention something about wanting to be farmers)
^(This place is a bit far from the city, but surely it would be a nice for the grandkids when they visit)
^(There doesn't seem to be a church nearby and the place overall is quite secluded)
^(Due to that there would be little option for a social life)
^(Would be a great spot for those who just want to get away however!)
^(I have one last place to checkout)
